SUMMARY:Aurora Realms
DESCRIPTION:Aurora Realms: A Gamer Convention for LGBTQIA2S+ & Allies\nJoin us for an unforgettable day of gaming\, community\, and creativity at Aurora Realms\, hosted by The Queen’s Guard!\nWhat to Expect:\n Guest Speakers – Hear from inspiring voices in gaming and LGBTQIA2S+ communities\n Vendors & Local Orgs – Explore unique merchandise and connect with community resources\n Cosplay Contest – Show off your best character look and win prizes\n RPG & Tabletop Games – Dive into epic adventures with fellow gamers\n Console Gaming – Play your favorite titles and discover new ones\n Giveaways – Win awesome swag throughout the day\nLGBTQIA2S+ gamers and allies of all ages! Whether you’re a tabletop strategist\, a console warrior\, or a cosplay enthusiast\, Aurora Realms is your space to celebrate geek culture and community.\n Level Up Your Pride – Join the Realm!\n\nBorough Community Gym\n350 E Dahlia Ave\, Palmer\, AK
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/aurora-realms/
END:VEVENT
