SUMMARY:Yellow Brick Road Quilt Class
DESCRIPTION:The “Yellow Brick Road” is a fun mix of rectangles and squares that is perfect for the beginning quilter. You will mix and match your pieces to make a quilt top that is sure to make you smile.\nOur class sample is made for the “In the Garden” fabric line and is displayed as a twin size. This pattern is Fat Quarter friendly and can be made in multiple sizes.\n810 S Colony Way \, Palmer
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/yellow-brick-road-quilt-class/
END:VEVENT
