SUMMARY:Hatcherpalooza
DESCRIPTION:It’s back! The biggest spring event in Hatcher Pass: Hatcherpalooza!\nThis free event includes our on-hill egg hunt (plus Golden Egg that wins the finder a season pass!)\, live music\, food trucks\, beer garden\, mid-mountain ski-mo race and slopestyle competition with prizes\, and more!\nEgg Hunt Information10:30 – 4:30: On-mountain egg hunt(Golden egg will be hidden on the hill. First person to find it wins a free 26/27 season pass!)\nMusic lineup12:30 – 2:00: Wiley Post2:30 – 4:00: Up a Mountain4:30 – 6:00: The River Livers\nSkiMo Race Information9:00: Pickup race bibs and day of registration9:45: Registration closes / Racer safety meeting10:15: SkiMo Race starts2:00: Awards ceremony (must be present to win)\nSlopestyle Competition Schedule:• 11:00am – Slopestyle Competition Check-in• 1:00pm – Slopestyle Competition Start• 4:30pm – Awards for Slopestyle\n13500 N. Skeetawk Circle\, Palmer
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/hatcherpalooza/
END:VEVENT
