SUMMARY:Consign49 Spring 2026 Consignment Sale
DESCRIPTION:Who is over this crazy winter and ready for Spring!!! Consign49 is back with our one stop shop for amazing deals on a selection of over 40\,000 clothing\, accessories\, and home decor items!\nJoin us this spring for our 26th semi-annual consignment pop-up\, being held at Raven Hall\, at the Alaska State Fairgrounds\, April 16-19!\nAdmission and parking are FREE! No tickets or reservation times are required except for during our presales on Wednesday\, April 15th!\nSale Schedule and Hours:Presales:Wednesday\, April 15th: (pass required\, tickets on sale mid-March)\nPublic Shopping:Thursday\, April 16th: 9am – 8pmFriday\, April 17th: 9am – 8pmSaturday\, April 18th: 9am – 6pmSunday\, April 19th: 9am – 5pm\, many items HALF PRICE!\nThis upscale resale shopping experience brings you great finds on new and gently used brand name and designer clothing\, accessories\, shoes\, home décor\, furniture\, and so much more!There is truly something for everyone.\nConsign49 is dependent upon our amazing consignors from the local community. Not only do consignors get to earn cash for items sold\, but they also get to shop presales before our pop-up opens to the public! Consignor Registration opens on February 11th at 10am! Spots are limited and expected to go quickly.\nTo find out more about how consigning works and how to register\, go to www.consign49.com/consign\nMake sure you are signed up for our email newsletter to get registration notifications\, sale date reminders and more! You can sign up directly from our website at www.consign49.com from the bottom of any page.\nWe hope to see you there!\n\nRaven Hall\n2075 S Glenn Hwy\, Palmer
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/consign49-spring-2026-consignment-sale/
END:VEVENT
