SUMMARY:Moonlight Gala
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by The Moonflower Boutique\, the Moonlight Gala is a 21+ ladies-only evening of elegance\, fun\, and connection. Join us at The Chalet at Government Peak on April 25\, 2026\, from 7 PM–11 PM for a night filled with dancing\, games\, prizes\, cocktails\, delicious bites\, and plenty of laughter. Dress to impress and enjoy an unforgettable night out with your community of women.\nTickets are $85per person and available in person at The Moonflower Boutique or online at: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/moonlight-gala-tickets-1980508479175?aff=oddtdtcreator&fbclid=IwY2xjawQYA6lleHRuA2FlbQIxMABicmlkETFWcVRJZ2ZQQzJwRGdxUnBpc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MgABHvK5LbksREjeuvSmKLLaTDLEke2foGPdCumJTYH5LrgvsDLtNhdfqj_UAv6N_aem_P4P4tbxkNzucQXSub2Isnw
