SUMMARY:Make it Take it Basket Party
DESCRIPTION:Come join us and make your own hanging basket to take home and enjoy. Everything is included for your 12″ basket. Plants\, basket\, soil and instruction. Cost is 79.00 It’s a wonderful hour spent in a beautiful greenhouse! Bring a Friend!\nAll classes are held at EweTopia Farms 3879 S Caudill in the Butte. Don’t believe the Facebook map. We do not have a facility in downtown Palmer.
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/make-it-take-it-basket-party/
