SUMMARY:Plant Sale by Palmer FFA
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Palmer FFA’s annual plant sale! We always open Mother’s Day weekend\, 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM Friday and Saturday\, at the Palmer High School Agriculture Building. Come get your annuals\, hanging baskets\, strawberries\, and veggies galore! If we don’t sell out\, we’ll be open a second weekend. Don’t miss out on a great event and supporting your local FFA chapter! \nPalmer High\, 1170 W. Bogard Rd. Palmer \n 
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/plant-sale-by-palmer-ffa/
