SUMMARY:Alaska Vintage Spring Market & Food Truck Fest "Enchanted Garden Theme"
DESCRIPTION:Come enjoy a fun weekend with friends and family! Shop some of Alaska’s trendiest small businesses\, up-cyclers\, designers\, and vintage collectors! We are also throwing a food truck festival with over 30 food vendors/truck. It’s going to be a blast! We love supporting other local Alaskan businesses and we hope you can come out and support them as well!\nThe first 100 VIP (weekend pass $10 EACH DAY bag with goodies)\nFriday 12-6 $5Saturday 10-6 $5Sunday 10-4 FreeTICKETS will be available soon.\nAlaska State Fairgrounds
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/alaska-vintage-spring-market-food-truck-fest-enchanted-garden-theme/
